<P>VIRGO TRIVMPHAN<GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="blotted" EXTENT="1 letter"> OR, VIRGINIA In Generall, but the South part therof in particular: Including the fertile CAROLANA, and the no lesse excellent Island of ROANOAK, richly and experimentally valued.</P>
<P>Humbly presented as the Auspice of a beginning Yeare, To the Parliament of ENGLAND, And Councell of STATE.</P>
<P>By EDVVARD WILLIAMS, Gent.</P>
<P>LONDON, Printed by THOMAS HARPER, for JOHN STEPHENSON, and are to be sold at his Shop on Ludgate-Hill, at the Signe of the Sunne, 1650.</P>
