<ITEM>Linseed oyle<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> 10l. the tun.</ITEM>
<ITEM>Saffron, 20s. the pound.</ITEM>
<ITEM>Honey, 2s. the gallon.</ITEM>
<ITEM>Waxe, 4l. the hundred.</ITEM>
