<ITEM>Sweet Gums, Roots, Woods, Berries for Dies and Drugs, send of all sorts as much as you can, every sort by it sel<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">e, there being great quantities of those things in Virginia, which after proof made, may be heere valued to their worth. And particularly, we have great hope of the Pocoon root, that it will prove better then Madder.</ITEM>
